  "id": "nofood",
  "name": "NoFood",
  "author": "DavyCraft648",
  "description": "Don't eat! You are fasting!",
  "readme_markdown": "# <img src=\"https://github.com/DavyCraft648/NoFood/blob/main/icon.png\" height=\"64\" width=\"64\"></img> NoFood\nDon't eat! You are fasting!\n\nThis plugin will **forbid** players to eat\n### Permission\n - nofood.bypass - Allow the player to eat - default: false\n \n### Config\n```yaml\n# NoFood plugin configuration file\n\n# No hungry feature: true|false\n# (NoFood feature is always on)\n#noHungry: false\nnoHungry: false\n\n# World folder name where the feature(s) is enabled\n# (case-sensitive)\n#worlds:\n#- worldName1\n#- worldName2\nworlds:\n- world\n- lobby\n\n# Consumable food\n# (or leave empty to make all food can't be eaten)\n#allowedFood:\n#- steak\n#- raw_chicken\n#- apple\nallowedFood: []\n```",
